"# systemctl disable nfs-server --now\n"
"# systemctl status nfs-server\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: UG9/en/linstor-gateway.adoc:144
msgid ""
"Ensure that the output of the command above lists the service as `inactive` "
"and `disabled`:"
